_sText: I think i might be getting a bit rusty with my mapping, but this is my first zombie map, and it has most of the stuff i would like a zombie map to have, moving doors, stuff to push infront of door ways, breakable windows, snow, a tall building with lots of rooms. Its a great map for window ledge hopping, u can basically get from any room to anyother just by jumping from window to window. :D give it a go xx
